 the pros we trust (and don’t) in high-pressure situations—game on the line, one bag to win, and everything in between. Big wins, shifting momentum, and a different kind of debate to end the show—this one’s a good mix of insight and fun." type="movie" contentRating="M/12" duration="3600000" originallyAvailableAt="2026-04-29T00:00:00Z" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/bbb/media_list/thumbnails/poster/2000x2858/around_the_acl_2by3.jpg" title="Around the ACL" userState="0" year="2026"><Image alt="Around the ACL" type="coverArt" url="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/bbb/media_list/thumbnails/widescreen/3840x2160/around_the_acl_16by9.jpg"/><Image alt="Around the ACL" type="coverPoster" url="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/bbb/media_list/thumbnails/poster/2000x2858/around_the_acl_2by3.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" id="620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" ratingKey="genre_620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" slug="sports" tag="Sports" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1777507200" duration="3600000" endsAt="1777510800" id="69e969ae4490591ef1341b1d" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/></Video><Video art="https://cdnapisec.kaltura.com/p/513551/sp/51355100/thumbnail/entry_id/1_e469bazf/version/0/vid_sec/5000/width/3840/height/2160/type/3/a.jpg" guid="plex://movie/69e969ad4490591ef1341aeb" key="/library/metadata/69e969ad4490591ef1341aeb" ratingKey="69e969ad4490591ef1341aeb" summary="Open 1: Women&apos;s, Juniors, Senior Singles from October 3, 2025" type="movie" contentRating="A" duration="18000000" originallyAvailableAt="2026-03-24T00:00:00Z" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://provider-static.plex.tv/epg/cms/production/1c897c1a-e779-4746-8845-c8625b2d91c0/Plex_cornhole_vertical_-_Brendan_Canning.jpg" title="25/26 ACL Rock Hill Open: Women&apos;s, Juniors, Senior Singles" userState="0" year="2026"><Image 